title: GS Blockchain
author: GS Blockchain
content: Recently, the representative team of Genesis had an in-depth exchange discussion wiht  Wisemont Capital to discuss the new commercial concept of ”consumption is investment” and Wisemont Capital believes that Genesis meets the real needs and pain points of the market, and provides a full range of technical supportstechnologies for a broader commercial ecosystem.Wisemont Capital is rooted in the two innovation centers of Silicon Valley and Seattle and foused  on the investment of first-tier enterprise projects in Silicon Valley. The investment fields include the Internet of Things, blockchain, artificial intelligence, B2B software, cloud technology, big data and etc.
